1.0.0.name: connect20/Comvos_ExtraCategoryTitle
1.0.0.description:
Adds an alternative page title to the category page.
So now you can have a different header on the category page than the navigation title.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
